/link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/after-donald-trumps-beijing-visit-taiwan-detects-8-chinese-naval-vessels-one-ship-in-its-territorial-water/articleshow/131130315.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-16T07:45:44+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131130440,imgsize-1104575.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Lil Tjay sparks backlash after exposing private messages linked to Kai Cenat’s ex-girlfriend]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131129821.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Lil Tjay sparked online backlash after briefly posting and deleting screenshots of private messages allegedly involving Kai Cenat’s ex-girlfriend, Gigi Alayah. Fans criticised the rapper for exposing personal conversations, while others defended his actions amid ongoing tension with Cenat. The streamer has not publicly responded, and the controversy has already reignited debates about clout-chasing, celebrity privacy, and social media drama in entertainment culture.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/lil-tjay-sparks-backlash-after-exposing-private-messages-linked-to-kai-cenats-ex-girlfriend/articleshow/131129821.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/lil-tjay-sparks-backlash-after-exposing-private-messages-linked-to-kai-cenats-ex-girlfriend/articleshow/131129821.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-16T05:32:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131129821,imgsize-44004.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[German Chancellor Friedrich Merz: I wouldn’t advise my kids to live or study in US]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131129911.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[German Chancellor Friedrich Merz advised his children against studying or working in the US due to a rapidly changing social climate and job market difficulties for the highly educated. Merz expressed strong optimism about Germany's opportunities for young people, contrasting it with his concerns about the current US situation.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/german-chancellor-friedrich-merz-i-wouldnt-advise-my-kids-to-live-or-study-in-us/articleshow/131129911.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/german-chancellor-friedrich-merz-i-wouldnt-advise-my-kids-to-live-or-study-in-us/articleshow/131129911.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-16T05:23:59+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131129909,imgsize-649053.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[What happened between Benny Johnson and Marjorie Taylor Greene? YouTuber faces grifting accusations during Thomas Massie controversy]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131129793.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Benny Johnson and Marjorie Taylor Greene became involved in a major online feud after Greene criticized Johnson’s YouTube coverage of hush-money allegations against Thomas Massie. The fight quickly turned personal, with both accusing each other of dishonesty and propaganda. Meanwhile, Massie strongly denied the accusations, calling them false and politically motivated just before his Kentucky primary election.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/what-happened-between-benny-johnson-and-marjorie-taylor-greene-youtuber-faces-grifting-accusations-during-thomas-massie-controversy/articleshow/131129793.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/what-happened-between-benny-johnson-and-marjorie-taylor-greene-youtuber-faces-grifting-accusations-during-thomas-massie-controversy/articleshow/131129793.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-16T04:23:28+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sehjal Gupta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131129789,imgsize-1066794.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Erika wanted his position": Candace Owens reacts after Charlie Kirk reportedly named wife Erika as TPUSA successor before assassination]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131129791.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens has questioned claims that Charlie Kirk chose wife Erika Kirk as his successor at Turning Point USA before his assassination. Owens cast doubt on the authenticity of an audio recording allegedly captured during a private Aspen donor retreat and demanded the release of full video footage. TPUSA has refused, citing donor privacy concerns, further fueling online debate and controversy.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/erika-wanted-his-position-candace-owens-reacts-after-charlie-kirk-reportedly-named-wife-erika-as-tpusa-successor-before-assassination/articleshow/131129791.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/erika-wanted-his-position-candace-owens-reacts-after-charlie-kirk-reportedly-named-wife-erika-as-tpusa-successor-before-assassination/articleshow/131129791.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-16T04:52:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/