><title><![CDATA[Trump-Xi summit ends with twist: US staff dump Chinese-issued phones, badges before boarding Air Force One]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131124646.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US staff and press accompanying President Trump reportedly discarded materials from Chinese officials before departing Beijing. This occurred despite public displays of goodwill, as behind-the-scenes tensions over security and media access surfaced during the visit, echoing past diplomatic friction.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-xi-summit-ends-with-twist-us-staff-dump-chinese-issued-phones-badges-before-boarding-air-force-one/articleshow/131124646.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-xi-summit-ends-with-twist-us-staff-dump-chinese-issued-phones-badges-before-boarding-air-force-one/articleshow/131124646.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-15T23:23:13+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131124909,imgsize-38590.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Meningitis outbreak in Berkshire causes panic in three schools]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131123741.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A student's death from meningitis at Henley College has prompted health officials to investigate links to Reading Blue Coat and Highdown Secondary schools. While the Berkshire strain differs from the Kent outbreak, authorities are providing precautionary treatment to close contacts. Experts emphasize the disease requires close contact to spread, with wider public risk remaining low.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/meningitis-outbreak-in-berkshire-causes-panic-in-three-schools/articleshow/131123741.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/meningitis-outbreak-in-berkshire-causes-panic-in-three-schools/articleshow/131123741.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-15T22:48:26+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131123839,imgsize-82500.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Michelle Obama: “When someone is cruel or acts like a bully, you don’t stoop to their level. No, our motto is…”]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131123618.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/quote-of-the-day-by-michelle-obama-when-someone-is-cruel-or-acts-like-a-bully-you-dont-stoop-to-their-level-no-our-motto-is/articleshow/131123618.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/quote-of-the-day-by-michelle-obama-when-someone-is-cruel-or-acts-like-a-bully-you-dont-stoop-to-their-level-no-our-motto-is/articleshow/131123618.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-15T22:47:52+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131123862,imgsize-46466.cms"/></item></channel></rss>